data.description: UPGRDES INCLUDING AC, WATER HEATER, 150 AMP MAIN PANEL BOX, ALL 150 PANELS.  ''Imagine stepping into your dream home as first-time buyers in the Amazing Misty Way Community. Nestled in the first cul de sac is this cozy 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven. Designed split floor plan that offers both privacy and comfort. One of the standout features of this gem is the screened porch that beckons you to unwind with a view of a spring-fed pond. This community offers more than just a house; it provides a lifestyle. With low HOA fees, you gain access to a refreshing community pool and tennis court. Brand-new AC unit and water heater, ensuring comfort and efficiency in every season. A screened 2-car garage offering a great breeze. In Misty Way, you'll find not just a house but a place to call home.
